{"key": "{\"messages\": [{\"content\": [{\"text\": \"Hello\", \"type\": \"text\"}], \"role\": \"user\"}], \"model\": \"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\", \"stop\": null, \"temperature\": 1.0, \"top_k\": null, \"top_p\": null}", "value": {"model": "claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929", "id": "msg_01WFJenwuvtb4fwvctKQoMNZ", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Hello! I'm Sculptor, an AI coding agent powered by Claude Code. I'm here to help you write code, fix bugs, and answer questions about your codebase.\n\nI can see you're currently on branch `branch_2` with a clean working directory. Your recent commits include adding tracked files and some work on `app.py`.\n\nHow can I help you today? Some things I can do:\n- Write or modify code\n- Debug issues\n- Refactor code\n- Explain how code works\n- Search through your codebase\n- Run tests and fix errors\n\nWhat would you like to work on?"}], "stop_reason": "end_turn", "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 3, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 3452, "cache_read_input_tokens": 12186, "cache_creation": {"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens": 3452, "ephemeral_1h_input_tokens": 0}, "output_tokens": 137, "service_tier": "standard"}}}
